{"pageid":114780,"pagename":"Tale of the Righteous/Quick guide","title":"Tale of the Righteous/Quick guide","displaytitle":"Tale of the Righteous/Quick guide","revid":14249355,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"notoc","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Congratulations, quest complete!"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"messagebox\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><span class=\"messagebox-title\"><b>This quick guide has an <a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous\" title=\"Tale of the Righteous\">in-depth guide here</a>.</b></span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\" class=\"messagebox-text\">It contains a more detailed description of dialogue, cutscenes, and storyline.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Speak to <a href=\"/w/Phileas_Rimor\" title=\"Phileas Rimor\">Phileas Rimor</a> in his house west of <a href=\"/w/The_Cloak_and_Stagger\" title=\"The Cloak and Stagger\">The Cloak and Stagger</a> tavern in <a href=\"/w/Shayzien\" title=\"Shayzien\">Shayzien</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Intermediate</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Over a thousand years ago, King Shayzien VII ordered an expedition to Mount Quidamortem. The expedition never returned and it was assumed that all members perished in the field. However, a recent discovery suggests this may not have been the case. Phileas Rimor is the descendant of the expedition leader and he is desperate to discover the truth. Join him and delve into a conspiracy a thousand years in the making in \"Tale of the Righteous\".</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\n<ul><li>Completion of the following quests:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Client_of_Kourend\" title=\"Client of Kourend\">Client of Kourend</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/X_Marks_the_Spot\" title=\"X Marks the Spot\">X Marks the Spot</a></li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Strength\" data-level=\"16\"><a href=\"/w/Strength\" title=\"Strength\"><img alt=\"Strength\" src=\"/images/Strength_icon.png?e6e0c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"16\" data-file-height=\"20\" /></a> 16 <a href=\"/w/Strength\" title=\"Strength\">Strength</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is not boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">not boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Mining\" data-level=\"10\"><a href=\"/w/Mining\" title=\"Mining\"><img alt=\"Mining\" src=\"/images/thumb/Mining_icon.png/21px-Mining_icon.png?00870\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Mining_icon.png?00870 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"23\" /></a> 10 <a href=\"/w/Mining\" title=\"Mining\">Mining</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is not boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">not boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li>20% <a href=\"/w/Shayzien\" title=\"Shayzien\">Shayzien</a> <a href=\"/w/Favour\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Favour\">favour</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li>A <a href=\"/w/Pickaxe\" title=\"Pickaxe\">pickaxe</a></li>\n<li>A <a href=\"/w/Ranged\" title=\"Ranged\">ranged</a> weapon with ammunition. Darts and throwing knives also work.</li>\n<li>Runes for 2-3 casts of any <a href=\"/w/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magic</a> <a href=\"/w/Combat_spell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Combat spell\">combat spell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Rope\" title=\"Rope\">Rope</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Combat level\" data-level=\"20\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\"><img alt=\"Combat level\" src=\"/images/Attack_style_icon.png?ceb2e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 20 <a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">Combat level</a></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Stamina_potion\" title=\"Stamina potion\">Stamina potion</a> and <a href=\"/w/Weight-reducing_clothing\" title=\"Weight-reducing clothing\">weight-reducing clothing</a></li>\n<li>Any kind of <a href=\"/w/Antipoison\" title=\"Antipoison\">antipoison</a> or <a href=\"/w/Shayzien_armour_(tier_5)\" title=\"Shayzien armour (tier 5)\">Shayzien armour (tier 5)</a> as you will encounter various types of poison dealing <a href=\"/w/Lizardman\" title=\"Lizardman\">Lizardman</a>, including the final boss.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> for low level players without a shortcut to the top of <a href=\"/w/Mount_Quidamortem\" title=\"Mount Quidamortem\">Mount Quidamortem</a></li>\n<li>Ability to use the <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_Minecart_Network\" title=\"Lovakengj Minecart Network\">Lovakengj Minecart Network</a> and <span class=\"coins coins-25 coins-pos\">50</span> to travel to <a href=\"/w/Mount_Quidamortem\" title=\"Mount Quidamortem\">Mount Quidamortem</a></li>\n<li>A charged <a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_talisman\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s talisman\">Xeric's talisman</a> for teleporting to <a href=\"/w/Mount_Quidamortem\" title=\"Mount Quidamortem\">Mount Quidamortem</a> (requires unlocking it with an <a href=\"/w/Ancient_tablet\" title=\"Ancient tablet\">Ancient tablet</a>) and <a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_Lookout\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s Lookout\">Xeric's Lookout</a>.</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<a href=\"/w/Corrupt_Lizardman\" title=\"Corrupt Lizardman\">Corrupt Lizardman</a> (level 46)</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;*Completion of the following quests:\\n**&#91;&#91;Client of Kourend&#93;&#93;\\n***&#91;&#91;X Marks the Spot&#93;&#93;\\n*&#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Strength\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;16\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Strength icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Strength|alt&#61;Strength&#93;&#93; 16 &#91;&#91;Strength&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is not boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;not boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;\\n*&#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Mining\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;10\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Mining icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Mining|alt&#61;Mining&#93;&#93; 10 &#91;&#91;Mining&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is not boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;not boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;\\n*20% &#91;&#91;Shayzien&#93;&#93; &#91;&#91;favour&#93;&#93;&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;Over a thousand years ago, King Shayzien VII ordered an expedition to Mount Quidamortem. The expedition never returned and it was assumed that all members perished in the field. However, a recent discovery suggests this may not have been the case. Phileas Rimor is the descendant of the expedition leader and he is desperate to discover the truth. Join him and delve into a conspiracy a thousand years in the making in \\&#34;Tale of the Righteous\\&#34;.&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Intermediate&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;&#91;&#91;Corrupt Lizardman&#93;&#93; (level 46)&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;Tale of the Righteous/Quick guide&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Speak to &#91;&#91;Phileas Rimor&#93;&#93; in his house west of &#91;&#91;The Cloak and Stagger&#93;&#93; tavern in &#91;&#91;Shayzien&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;*A &#91;&#91;pickaxe&#93;&#93;\\n*A &#91;&#91;ranged&#93;&#93; weapon with ammunition. Darts and throwing knives also work.\\n*Runes for 2-3 casts of any &#91;&#91;magic&#93;&#93; &#91;&#91;combat spell&#93;&#93;\\n*&#91;&#91;Rope&#93;&#93;&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go to the house west of the <a href=\"/w/The_Cloak_and_Stagger\" title=\"The Cloak and Stagger\">The Cloak and Stagger</a> tavern in <a href=\"/w/Shayzien\" title=\"Shayzien\">Shayzien</a>. (<a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_Talisman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s Talisman\">Xeric's Talisman</a> - 1. Xeric's Lookout and run north-west)</li>\n<li>Speak to <a href=\"/w/Phileas_Rimor\" title=\"Phileas Rimor\">Phileas Rimor</a>, and agree to help him. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Do you need help with anything?\">2</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-66f078e1a0dc4502e7f896d6df049796\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-66f078e1a0dc4502e7f896d6df049796\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>2</b></td><td>Do you need help with anything?</td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Gather a ranged weapon, a melee weapon (a pickaxe counts as a valid melee weapon), and runes to perform any magic attack if you have not already.</li>\n<li>Go to the <a href=\"/w/Arceuus_Library\" title=\"Arceuus Library\">Arceuus Library</a> (Fairy ring <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>C</b><b>I</b><b>S</b></span> (if unlocked) or <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_Minecart_Network\" title=\"Lovakengj Minecart Network\">Lovakengj Minecart Network</a>) and speak to <a href=\"/w/Archeio\" title=\"Archeio\">Archeio</a> to teleport to the <a href=\"/w/Library_Historical_Archive\" title=\"Library Historical Archive\">Library Historical Archive</a>.</li>\n<li>Speak to <a href=\"/w/Pagida\" title=\"Pagida\">Pagida</a>, and agree to be teleported into the <a href=\"/w/Tower_of_Magic\" title=\"Tower of Magic\">Tower of Magic</a> prison. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I have a question about King Shayzien VII.\">2</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes please.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-b1fbeae6269c4acd168f9e3085df087c\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-b1fbeae6269c4acd168f9e3085df087c\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>2</b></td><td>I have a question about King Shayzien VII.</td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes please.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Push the strange device all the way west. From the north side, attack the device using magic.</li>\n<li>From the south side, attack using melee.</li>\n<li>Push the strange device all the way east. From the south side, attack using ranged.</li>\n<li>Investigate the skeleton in the northern cell.</li>\n<li>Return to the quest start and talk to <a href=\"/w/Phileas_Rimor\" title=\"Phileas Rimor\">Phileas Rimor</a> (<a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_Talisman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s Talisman\">Xeric's Talisman</a> - 1. Xeric's Lookout and run north-west).</li>\n<li>Go north-west to the <a href=\"/w/War_Tent\" title=\"War Tent\">War Tent</a> in the south-west corner of the <a href=\"/w/Shayzien_Encampment\" title=\"Shayzien Encampment\">Shayzien Encampment</a>. Go upstairs and speak to <a href=\"/w/Lord_Shiro_Shayzien\" title=\"Lord Shiro Shayzien\">Lord Shiro Shayzien</a>.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:382px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Path_to_Raids.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Path_to_Raids.png/380px-Path_to_Raids.png?0c616\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"380\" height=\"302\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Path_to_Raids.png/570px-Path_to_Raids.png?0c616 1.5x, /images/thumb/Path_to_Raids.png/760px-Path_to_Raids.png?0c616 2x\" data-file-width=\"1007\" data-file-height=\"799\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Path_to_Raids.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Getting to Mount Quidamortem from the <a href=\"/w/Shayziens%27_Wall\" title=\"Shayziens&#39; Wall\">Shayziens' Wall</a>.</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Travel to the summit of <a href=\"/w/Mount_Quidamortem\" title=\"Mount Quidamortem\">Mount Quidamortem</a>. (<a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_Minecart_Network\" title=\"Lovakengj Minecart Network\">Lovakengj Minecart Network</a> or <a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_Talisman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s Talisman\">Xeric's Talisman</a> - 5. Xeric's Honour if it is unlocked)\n<ul><li>(Optional) Speak to the <a href=\"/w/Mountain_Guide\" title=\"Mountain Guide\">Mountain Guide</a> to unlock quick travel to and from the mountain.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Speak to <a href=\"/w/Historian_Duffy\" title=\"Historian Duffy\">Historian Duffy</a>. (near the water symbol on the minimap)</li>\n<li>Use a rope on the crevice on the western side of the mountain, and enter the crevice. Go around to the south, not through the middle. (near the&#160;! symbol on minimap)</li>\n<li>Mine the Boulder.</li>\n<li>Push the Boulder.</li>\n<li>Attempt to pass the magic gate, and kill the <a href=\"/w/Corrupt_Lizardman\" title=\"Corrupt Lizardman\">Corrupt Lizardman</a>.</li>\n<li>Pass through the magic gate and inspect the <a href=\"/w/Unstable_Altar\" title=\"Unstable Altar\">Unstable Altar</a>.</li>\n<li>Hop worlds after you finish the dialogue to quickly leave the cave.</li>\n<li>Speak to Historian Duffy again.</li>\n<li>Go back to the unstable altar in the cave.</li>\n<li>Speak to Duffy and then <a href=\"/w/Gnosi\" title=\"Gnosi\">Gnosi</a> near the unstable altar. Make sure to speak to them BOTH.</li>\n<li>Speak to Lord Shiro Shayzien back at the war tent. (Fairy ring <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>D</b><b>J</b><b>R</b></span> or the <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_Minecart_Network\" title=\"Lovakengj Minecart Network\">Lovakengj Minecart Network</a>)</li>\n<li>Return to Phileas's house and walk inside to get dialogue. He will not be there.</li>\n<li>Return to Lord Shiro Shayzien once more.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><b>Congratulations, quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Tale_of_the_Righteous_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tale of the Righteous reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Tale_of_the_Righteous_reward_scroll.png?11d80\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>1 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest point</a></li>\n<li>8,000 <a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\">coins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Shayzien_favour_certificate\" title=\"Shayzien favour certificate\">Shayzien favour certificate</a>. Reading it grants 10% <a href=\"/w/Shayzien\" title=\"Shayzien\">Shayzien</a> favour.</li>\n<li>A page for <a href=\"/w/Kharedst%27s_memoirs\" title=\"Kharedst&#39;s memoirs\">Kharedst's memoirs</a>, '<a href=\"/w/History_and_hearsay\" title=\"History and hearsay\">History and hearsay</a>.' It teleports players to the <a href=\"/w/Graveyard_of_Heroes\" title=\"Graveyard of Heroes\">Graveyard of Heroes</a> south-west of the Shayzien bank.</li>\n<li>Ability to fight the <a href=\"/w/Corrupt_Lizardman\" title=\"Corrupt Lizardman\">Corrupt Lizardman</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Nightmare_Zone\" title=\"Nightmare Zone\">Nightmare Zone</a>.</li>\n<li>3 <a href=\"/w/Xerician_fabric\" title=\"Xerician fabric\">Xerician fabric</a> (dropped by Corrupt Lizardman)</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Tale of the Righteous\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Tale_of_the_Righteous\" title=\"Template:Tale of the Righteous\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Tale_of_the_Righteous\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Tale_of_the_Righteous?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Tale_of_the_Righteous\" title=\"Tale of the Righteous\">Tale of the Righteous</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-parent\" style=\"padding:0\"><table class=\"navbox-subgroup nowraplinks\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr class=\"navbox-group navbox-group-split\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title-hidden\" colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none\"></td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Phileas_Rimor\" title=\"Phileas Rimor\"><img alt=\"Phileas Rimor chathead.png: Chat head image of Phileas Rimor\" src=\"/images/thumb/Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png/30px-Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png?3b5ef\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png/46px-Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png?3b5ef 1.5x, /images/thumb/Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png/61px-Phileas_Rimor_chathead.png?3b5ef 2x\" data-file-width=\"85\" data-file-height=\"98\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Phileas_Rimor\" title=\"Phileas Rimor\">Phileas Rimor</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lord_Shiro_Shayzien\" title=\"Lord Shiro Shayzien\"><img alt=\"Lord Shiro Shayzien chathead.png: Chat head image of Lord Shiro Shayzien\" src=\"/images/thumb/Lord_Shiro_Shayzien_chathead.png/26px-Lord_Shiro_Shayzien_chathead.png?6744f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"26\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Lord_Shiro_Shayzien_chathead.png/40px-Lord_Shiro_Shayzien_chathead.png?6744f 1.5x, /images/thumb/Lord_Shiro_Shayzien_chathead.png/53px-Lord_Shiro_Sha