pt Lizardman\">Corrupt Lizardman</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Items</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Dusty_note\" title=\"Dusty note\"><img alt=\"Dusty note.png\" src=\"/images/Dusty_note.png?5eb13\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Dusty_note\" title=\"Dusty note\">Dusty note</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Rewards</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Shayzien_favour_certificate\" title=\"Shayzien favour certificate\"><img alt=\"Shayzien favour certificate.png\" src=\"/images/Shayzien_favour_certificate.png?f410d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Shayzien_favour_certificate\" title=\"Shayzien favour certificate\">Shayzien favour certificate</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/History_and_hearsay\" title=\"History and hearsay\"><img alt=\"History and hearsay.png\" src=\"/images/History_and_hearsay.png?53fc0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/History_and_hearsay\" title=\"History and hearsay\">History and hearsay</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Shayzien\" title=\"Shayzien\">Shayzien</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Library_Historical_Archive\" title=\"Library Historical Archive\">Library Historical Archive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Tower_of_Magic\" title=\"Tower of Magic\">Tower of Magic</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Mount_Quidamortem\" title=\"Mount Quidamortem\">Mount Quidamortem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Quidamortem_Cave\" title=\"Quidamortem Cave\">Quidamortem Cave</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:Tale_of_the_Righteous\" title=\"Transcript:Tale of the Righteous\">Transcript</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Cyan_crystal_(Tale_of_the_Righteous)\" title=\"Cyan crystal (Tale of the Righteous)\"><img alt=\"Cyan crystal (Tale of the Righteous).png\" src=\"/images/Cyan_crystal_%28Tale_of_the_Righteous%29.png?fe45d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"28\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"28\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Cyan_crystal_(Tale_of_the_Righteous)\" title=\"Cyan crystal (Tale of the Righteous)\">Cyan crystal</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐tvfj6\nCached time: 20220512015247\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.205 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.300 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 451/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 34628/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5426/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1228905/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  217.991      1 -total\n 50.37%  109.812      1 Template:Quest_details_page\n 16.87%   36.769      2 Template:Checklist\n 15.02%   32.738      1 Template:Quest_rewards_page\n 13.86%   30.212      2 Template:Navbox\n 12.89%   28.094      1 Template:Tale_of_the_Righteous\n  9.42%   20.541      2 Template:Chat_option\n  4.63%   10.093      1 Template:Quick_Guide\n  4.10%    8.930      3 Template:Ctg\n  2.83%    6.159      2 Template:Fairycode\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:114780-0!canonical and timestamp 20220512015246 and revision id 14249355. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{Quick Guide}}\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details page|Tale of the Righteous}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n{{Checklist|\n*Go to the house west of the [[The Cloak and Stagger]] tavern in [[Shayzien]]. ([[Xeric's Talisman]] - 1. Xeric's Lookout and run north-west)\n*Speak to [[Phileas Rimor]], and agree to help him. {{Chat option|2Do you need help with anything?|1Yes.}}\n*Gather a ranged weapon, a melee weapon (a pickaxe counts as a valid melee weapon), and runes to perform any magic attack if you have not already.\n*Go to the [[Arceuus Library]] (Fairy ring {{Fairycode|CIS}} (if unlocked) or [[Lovakengj Minecart Network]]) and speak to [[Archeio]] to teleport to the [[Library Historical Archive]].\n*Speak to [[Pagida]], and agree to be teleported into the [[Tower of Magic]] prison. {{Chat option|2I have a question about King Shayzien VII.|1Yes please.}}\n*Push the strange device all the way west. From the north side, attack the device using magic.\n*From the south side, attack using melee.\n*Push the strange device all the way east. From the south side, attack using ranged.\n*Investigate the skeleton in the northern cell.\n*Return to the quest start and talk to [[Phileas Rimor]] ([[Xeric's Talisman]] - 1. Xeric's Lookout and run north-west).\n*Go north-west to the [[War Tent]] in the south-west corner of the [[Shayzien Encampment]]. Go upstairs and speak to [[Lord Shiro Shayzien]].\n}}\n[[File:Path to Raids.png|thumb|380px|Getting to Mount Quidamortem from the [[Shayziens' Wall]].]]\n{{Checklist|\n*Travel to the summit of [[Mount Quidamortem]]. ([[Lovakengj Minecart Network]] or [[Xeric's Talisman]] - 5. Xeric's Honour if it is unlocked)\n**(Optional) Speak to the [[Mountain Guide]] to unlock quick travel to and from the mountain.\n*Speak to [[Historian Duffy]]. (near the water symbol on the minimap) \n*Use a rope on the crevice on the western side of the mountain, and enter the crevice. Go around to the south, not through the middle. (near the ! symbol on minimap)\n*Mine the Boulder.\n*Push the Boulder.\n*Attempt to pass the magic gate, and kill the [[Corrupt Lizardman]].\n*Pass through the magic gate and inspect the [[Unstable Altar]].\n*Hop worlds after you finish the dialogue to quickly leave the cave.\n*Speak to Historian Duffy again.\n*Go back to the unstable altar in the cave.\n*Speak to Duffy and then [[Gnosi]] near the unstable altar. Make sure to speak to them BOTH.\n*Speak to Lord Shiro Shayzien back at the war tent. (Fairy ring {{Fairycode|DJR}} or the [[Lovakengj Minecart Network]])\n*Return to Phileas's house and walk inside to get dialogue. He will not be there.\n*Return to Lord Shiro Shayzien once more.\n}}\n\n'''Congratulations, quest complete!'''\n\n==Rewards==\n{{Quest rewards page|Tale of the Righteous}}\n\n{{Tale of the Righteous}}"}